<STARTDOC>
macro(abstract(text))
 (Defines an abstract for an article or report type of document. Abstracts are
not implemented for books or manpages. Must appear bf(before) starting the
document using the tt(article) or tt(report) macro.
 )
<>

DEFINEMACRO(abstract)(1)(\
    SETSYMBOL(XXabstracttext)(ARG1)\
)

